                            <comment id="12982399" author="moczarski" created="Sun, 16 Jan 2011 22:16:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This patch depends on &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/AMQ-3140&quot; title=&quot;Lost messages when scheduling messages concurrently&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;AMQ-3140&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;AMQ-3140&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; because the schedule method must be synchronized so that the main loop use the same lock.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
